    This class handles the salary calculations for employees, including tax calculations (USC, PRSI, PAYE), loading pay scales and rates from a CSV file, and processing employee data.

    PartTimeHourCalculator
    The PartTimeHourCalculator class is responsible for calculating the earned amount for part-time employees based on their department, role, and hours worked.

    This class moves all employees up the payscale for their respective jobs.

    This class allows payslips to be generated for all employees.
